ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How often are coin prices updated?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app updates coin prices in real-time, ensuring you always have access to the most current market data for informed decision-making.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We support a wide range of cryptocurrencies, including major coins like Bitcoin and Ethereum, as well as numerous altcoins. Our list is constantly expanding to cover the dynamic crypto market.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, you can easily set custom price alerts for any coin in our app. Receive notifications when your chosen cryptocurrencies reach specific price points, helping you stay on top of market movements.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our basic version is completely free, providing essential coin price information. We also offer a premium version with advanced features for more dedicated crypto enthusiasts and traders.
